Package tk.artsakenos.iperunits.file

Interface FileDrop.TransferableObject.Fetcher

Enclosing class:
FileDrop.TransferableObject
public static interface FileDrop.TransferableObject.Fetcher
Instead of passing your data directly to the FileDrop.TransferableObject constructor, you may want to know exactly when your data was received in case you need to remove it from its source (or do anyting else to it). When the getTransferData(...) method is called on the FileDrop.TransferableObject, the FileDrop.TransferableObject.Fetcher's getObject() method will be called.
